 BEC condensation momenta instead of by any\ndifferences in the symmetry breaking patterns. All these novel quantum or\ntopological phenomena can be probed in the recent experimentally realized\nweakly interacting Quantum Anomalous Hall (QAH) model of $ ^87 Rb $ by Wu, {\\sl\net.al}, Science 354, 83-88 (2016).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Nov 2017 18:53:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-12-01"}
