, and the\ncharacteristic surface states of the resulting TCIs.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 30 Nov 2017 18:59:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Feb 2018 05:11:16 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 18 Sep 2018 02:26:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-19"}
