d Tomamichel from [Wilde,\nTomamichel, Berta, IEEE Trans. Inf. Theory 63(3):1792, March 2017].\nFurthermore, I show that it is not necessary to invoke the energy-constrained\ndiamond distance in order to confirm the correctness of this proof.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 1 Dec 2017 01:26:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 Dec 2017 19:38:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 26 Dec 2017 18:31:37 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 2 Jan 2018 17:45:19 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Tue, 5 Jun 2018 14:10:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-09"}
